{
  "info": {
    "name": "Solar Energy Metrics API",
    "description": "API Collection for Solar Energy Performance Calculations\n\nEndpoints:\n1. GET /device/:deviceId/solar-metrics - Calculate Daily PR and CUF",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Solar Metrics",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Calculate Solar Metrics",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/device/1/solar-metrics?fromDate=2026-02-10&toDate=2026-02-12&tiltAngle=18&diffuseFraction=0.2&albedo=0.2",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "device",
                "1",
                "solar-metrics"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "fromDate",
                  "value": "2026-02-10",
                  "description": "Start date in format YYYY-MM-DD (optional, defaults to today)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "toDate",
                  "value": "2026-02-12",
                  "description": "End date in format YYYY-MM-DD (optional, defaults to today)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "tiltAngle",
                  "value": "18",
                  "description": "Module tilt angle in degrees (optional, default: 18)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "diffuseFraction",
                  "value": "0.2",
                  "description": "Diffuse fraction (optional, default: 0.2, typical range 0.15-0.25)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "albedo",
                  "value": "0.2",
                  "description": "Ground reflectance/albedo (optional, default: 0.2)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Calculate solar energy performance metrics including Performance Ratio (PR) and Capacity Utilization Factor (CUF) for a device.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `deviceId` (required): Device ID\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `fromDate` (optional): Start date (YYYY-MM-DD), defaults to today\n- `toDate` (optional): End date (YYYY-MM-DD), defaults to today\n- `tiltAngle` (optional): Module tilt angle in degrees (default: 18°)\n- `diffuseFraction` (optional): Diffuse fraction (default: 0.2)\n- `albedo` (optional): Ground reflectance (default: 0.2)\n\n**Authentication:** Bearer Token (JWT)\n\n**Calculations Performed:**\n1. Irradiance Components\n   - Diffuse: GHI × fd × (1+cosβ)/2\n   - Reflected: GHI × ρ × (1−cosβ)/2\n   - Beam: GHI − (Id + Ir)\n   - Total POA: Ib + Id + Ir\n\n2. Performance Ratio (PR)\n   - PR = (Eac / Pdc) / (GHI / 1) × 100 (%)\n\n3. Capacity Utilization Factor (CUF)\n   - CUF = (Total Energy / Plant Capacity × 24 × Days) × 100 (%)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success Response",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/device/1/solar-metrics?fromDate=2026-02-10&toDate=2026-02-12&tiltAngle=18&diffuseFraction=0.2&albedo=0.2",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "device",
                    "1",
                    "solar-metrics"
                  ],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "fromDate",
                      "value": "2026-02-10"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "toDate",
                      "value": "2026-02-12"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "tiltAngle",
                      "value": "18"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "diffuseFraction",
                      "value": "0.2"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "albedo",
                      "value": "0.2"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"device\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"sn\": \"DEVICE-SN-001\",\n    \"type\": \"INVERTER\"\n  },\n  \"station\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Solar Station 1\",\n    \"location\": \"New Delhi, India\",\n    \"installedCapacity\": 10.355,\n    \"unit\": \"kWp\"\n  },\n  \"period\": {\n    \"from\": \"2026-02-10\",\n    \"to\": \"2026-02-12\",\n    \"days\": 3,\n    \"dataPoints\": 72\n  },\n  \"aggregatedData\": {\n    \"totalACEnergy\": 681.9,\n    \"averageGHI\": 5.268,\n    \"unit\": \"kWh, kWh/m²\"\n  },\n  \"calculations\": {\n    \"diffuse\": 1.027816573,\n    \"reflected\": 0.025783427,\n    \"beam\": 4.2144,\n    \"totalPOA\": 5.268\n  },\n  \"results\": {\n    \"performanceRatio\": {\n      \"value\": 72.5937642,\n      \"unit\": \"%\",\n      \"description\": \"Daily Performance Ratio\"\n    },\n    \"capacityUtilizationFactor\": {\n      \"value\": 17.1,\n      \"unit\": \"%\",\n      \"description\": \"Capacity Utilization Factor\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"detailedTimeSeries\": [\n    {\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\n      \"acEnergy\": 25.5,\n      \"ghi\": 4.8,\n      \"weather\": {\n        \"temp\": 28.5,\n        \"clouds\": 15\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-10T01:00:00.000Z\",\n      \"acEnergy\": 28.3,\n      \"ghi\": 5.2,\n      \"weather\": {\n        \"temp\": 29.1,\n        \"clouds\": 10\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"calculatedAt\": \"2026-02-12T10:30:45.123Z\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Device Not Found",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/device/999/solar-metrics",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
